      "summary": [],
      "legalText": {
        "preamble": "THIS CONTRACT for the personal services of musicians, made this day of {TODAY}, between the undersigned Purchaser (hereinafter called the 'Purchaser') and {numberOfMusicians} musician(s) (hereinafter called the 'Musicians'). The Purchaser hereby employs the personal services of the Musicians, and the Musicians hereby agree to render collectively and in behalf of the undersigned Leader, their services as musicians in the orchestra under the leadership of {leaderName}.",
        "clause1": "The terms and conditions of this contract shall be in accordance with all the rules and regulations of the American Federation of Musicians and its affiliated Local in whose jurisdiction the engagement is to be performed.",
        "clause2_Recording": "No performance of the engagement shall be recorded, reproduced, or transmitted from the place of performance in any manner or by any means whatsoever, in the absence of a specific written agreement with the Federation relating to and permitting such recording, reproduction, or transmission.",
        "clause_arbitrationL1": "All claims, disputes, or controversies arising out of or in connection with this agreement shall be submitted for final and binding resolution to the Executive Board of the Local Union in whose jurisdiction the services were performed, or to the American Arbitration Association, at the Purchaser's election.",
        "clause_courtActionL2": "Any claims, disputes, or controversies arising out of or in connection with this agreement shall be adjudicated in a court of competent jurisdiction."
      }
